Package: ranim
Title: Hierarchical Shape-Based Animations in R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Justin",
      family = "Landis",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "jtlandis314@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Tools for creating hierarchical, shape-based animations in R.
    Shapes can contain other shapes and can be manipulated over time with
    composable "action" objects. Animations are rendered frame-by-frame and
    can be exported as GIFs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://example.org/ranim
BugReports: https://example.org/ranim/issues
